title: #63 - Ninja
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast we are joined by twitch streamer/pro-gamer/Drake's BFF- Tyler Blevins aka Ninja! Together we discuss Fortnite, Drake, E-Sports, home defense with katanas, and bidets. Ninja is the current biggest star on twitch, streaming Fortnite to his over 6 millions followers.
